<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今晚就是萬聖節了！<delay frames="40" />
真不枉費我做了那麼多準備～<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我今天想盡情享受萬聖節，<delay20 />
所以<delay8 />得在傍晚前
<anim id="Assent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />把該做的事情做完才行，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />終於正式迎來<delay8 />萬聖節當天了。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我已經迫不及待地想享受節慶了喔！<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />既然是萬聖節，<delay8 />
那我就來做加入了南瓜的
<tag a="135" b="7" arg="0xcd00" />吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你會參加今天的萬聖節活動嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我很期待<delay20 />能收到你的糖果，<delay8 />
所以到時候如果能見到你的話，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那就太好了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />現在是<delay20 /><tag a="90" b="33" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Surprised" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也就是說，萬聖節
就快要開始了！？
<anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哇～<delay20 />我開始緊張起來了！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />喝點<tag a="135" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /><delay8 />
來冷靜一下好了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00">馬上就是萬聖節了呢。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我感到有點害怕，又有點期待<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我現在心臟跳得超快的……<delay8 />
<tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />到時候請你手下留情喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />到了5點，<delay8 />萬聖節就要開始囉。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我得先把糖果帶在身上才行！<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不知道大家會裝扮成什麼樣子<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我稍後也會換衣服，<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />敬請期待喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="100" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />對了對了，<delay frames="30" />我有在島上
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看到南瓜裝飾喔。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />已經到萬聖節的季節了呢～<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我很期待<delay8 />萬聖節的到來，<delay8 />
而且很喜歡南瓜，<delay8 /><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以我一看到
萬聖節裝飾就覺得很興奮喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看到這麼多的南瓜裝飾，
讓人<delay8 />越來越興奮了！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我好期待萬聖節啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">這座島上的南瓜裝飾<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />還真是增加了不少呢～<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />再這樣繼續增加下去
會變得怎麼樣呢？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊～<delay20 />我好期待喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay8 />好厲害喔！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不管走到哪<delay20 />都是南瓜裝飾<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="33" />已經完全<delay20 />
染上萬聖節的氣氛了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>